⚠️ ATENÇÃO: O generator no schema.prisma deve usar provider = "prisma-client-js" (não "prisma-client"). Se novos campos não aparecerem no client gerado após o generate, deletar src/generated e rodar npx prisma generate novamente:
powershellRemove-Item -Recurse -Force src\generated
npx prisma generate
Schema Prisma — COMPLETO E ATUAL
prismagenerator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
  output   = "../generated/prisma"
}

datasource db {
  provider = "postgresql"
}

enum Role { ADMIN PERSONAL STUDENT }
enum StudentStatus { ACTIVE INACTIVE OVERDUE }
enum PaymentStatus { PAID PENDING OVERDUE }
enum PlanType { MONTHLY QUARTERLY SEMIANNUAL ANNUAL }

model User {
  id           String        @id @default(uuid())
  name         String
  email        String        @unique
  password     String
  role         Role          @default(PERSONAL)
  createdAt    DateTime      @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime      @updatedAt
  student      Student?
  workoutPlans WorkoutPlan[]
}

model Student {
  id           String        @id @default(uuid())
  userId       String        @unique
  user         User          @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id])
  phone        String?
  birthDate    DateTime?
  goal         String?
  plan         PlanType      @default(MONTHLY)
  status       StudentStatus @default(ACTIVE)
  createdAt    DateTime      @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime      @updatedAt
  payments     Payment[]
  bodyRecords  BodyRecord[]
  workoutPlans WorkoutPlan[]
}

model Payment {
  id        String        @id @default(uuid())
  studentId String
  student   Student       @relation(fields: [studentId], references: [id])
  amount    Decimal       @db.Decimal(10, 2)
  dueDate   DateTime
  paidAt    DateTime?
  status    PaymentStatus @default(PENDING)
  note      String?
  createdAt DateTime      @default(now())
}

model WorkoutPlan {
  id          String            @id @default(uuid())
  studentId   String
  student     Student           @relation(fields: [studentId], references: [id])
  createdById String
  createdBy   User              @relation(fields: [createdById], references: [id])
  name        String
  description String?
  active      Boolean           @default(true)
  createdAt   DateTime          @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime          @updatedAt
  exercises   WorkoutExercise[]
}

model Exercise {
  id           String            @id @default(uuid())
  name         String
  muscleGroup  String
  description  String?
  gifUrl       String?
  createdAt    DateTime          @default(now())
  workoutItems WorkoutExercise[]
}

model WorkoutExercise {
  id            String      @id @default(uuid())
  workoutPlanId String
  workoutPlan   WorkoutPlan @relation(fields: [workoutPlanId], references: [id])
  exerciseId    String
  exercise      Exercise    @relation(fields: [exerciseId], references: [id])
  sets          Int
  reps          String
  load          String?
  rest          String?
  order         Int
}

model BodyRecord {
  id         String   @id @default(uuid())
  studentId  String
  student    Student  @relation(fields: [studentId], references: [id])
  weight     Decimal? @db.Decimal(5, 2)
  height     Decimal? @db.Decimal(4, 2)
  bodyFat    Decimal? @db.Decimal(4, 2)
  notes      String?
  recordedAt DateTime @default(now())
}
Endpoints (27+ rotas)
Auth (públicas)

POST /session — login, retorna { token, user: { id, name, email, role, studentId } }
POST /users — criar usuário

Perfil (Authenticated)

GET /me — retorna dados do usuário + studentId: user.student?.id ?? null
PUT /me — atualizar perfil
PATCH /me/password — trocar senha

Alunos (Authenticated)

POST /students — cadastrar aluno + gerar pagamentos automáticos
GET /students — listar (filtros: status, plano)
GET /students/:id — detalhe com fichas e pagamentos
PUT /students/:id — editar
DELETE /students/:id — remover [isAdmin]
GET /students/overdue — inadimplentes

Pagamentos (Authenticated)

POST /students/:id/payments — registrar pagamento avulso
GET /students/:id/payments — histórico do aluno
GET /payments — listar todos com filtro ?status=
PATCH /payments/:id/status — marcar PAID ou OVERDUE
GET /payments/upcoming — vencendo em 7 dias

Fichas de Treino (Authenticated)

POST /students/:id/workout-plans — criar ficha
GET /students/:id/workout-plans — listar fichas do aluno
GET /workout-plans/:id — detalhe com exercícios
PUT /workout-plans/:id — editar
DELETE /workout-plans/:id — remover
PATCH /workout-plans/:id/activate — ativar (desativa as demais)

Exercícios (Authenticated / isAdmin para write)

POST /exercises — criar com gifUrl [isAdmin]
GET /exercises — listar (busca por nome/grupo muscular)
PUT /exercises/:id — editar [isAdmin]
DELETE /exercises/:id — remover [isAdmin]

Dashboard (Authenticated)

GET /dashboard/metrics — total alunos, receita mês, inadimplentes, novos alunos

Lógica de Negócio
Pagamentos automáticos ao cadastrar aluno:

MONTHLY: 1x R$99,90
QUARTERLY: 3x R$89,97
SEMIANNUAL: 6x R$83,32
ANNUAL: 12x R$74,99
Todos com status PENDING, vencimento dia 1 de cada mês

SessionService — retorna studentId:
typescriptreturn { token, user: { id, name, email, role, studentId: user.student?.id ?? null } }
MeService — retorna studentId:
typescriptselect: { id, name, email, role, createdAt, student: { select: { id: true } } }
return { ...user, studentId: user.student?.id ?? null }
```

**Ativação de ficha:** PATCH /workout-plans/:id/activate desativa todas as outras fichas do aluno antes de ativar a nova.

## Permissões por Role
- ADMIN: acesso total
- PERSONAL: tudo exceto deletar alunos e gerenciar exercícios
- STUDENT: apenas /minha-area (área do aluno)

